:INFO
Set Up Your Workspace Safely
Always burn in a well-ventilated space or directly under an exhaust fan. Wood smoke \
contains particulates that accumulate in the lungs over time. Keep a small fan blowing \
smoke away from your face, not across the work surface. Wear a basic respirator if

