Temperature, Wood, and Tip Type
Wire nib burners heat and cool quickly and give you fine control.
|
:INFO
Temperature, Wood, and Tip Type
Wire nib burners heat and cool quickly and give you fine control. Solid tip burners stay \
hot longer and suit broader shading. Start at a medium temperature and test on scrap \
from the same board. A universal writing tip works for lines. A shader tip

